'''Google涂鸦'''（{{lang-en|Google Doodle}}）是为庆祝[[节日|节日]]、纪念日、成就以及纪念杰出人物等而对[[Google|Google]][[首页|首页]][[Google商標|商标]]的一种特殊的临时变更。Google的第一个[[塗鴉|涂鸦]]是在1998年为[[火人祭|火人祭]]活動设计的。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.google.com/doodle4google/history.html |title=Doodle 4 Google |publisher=Google.com |date= |accessdate=2014-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140427143948/http://www.google.com/doodle4google/history.html |archive-date=2014-04-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.google.com/doodles/burning-man-festival |title=Burning Man Festival |publisher=Google.com |date=1998-08-30 |accessdate=2014-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140425051111/https://www.google.com/doodles/burning-man-festival |archive-date=2014-04-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>这个徽标由[[拉里·佩奇|拉里·佩奇]]和[[谢尔盖·布林|谢尔盖·布林]]亲自设计。此后Google的节日涂鸦都采用设计[[外包|外包]]模式。2000年佩奇和布林让实习生[[黄正穆|黄正穆]]设计[[巴士底日|巴士底日]]的涂鸦。从这时开始，涂鸦开始由“Doodlers”团队的员工管理和发布。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2014/apr/12/meet-people-behind-google-doodles-logo|title=Meet the people behind the Google Doodles|publisher=The Guardian|date=2014-04-12|accessdate=2014-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006222909/http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2014/apr/12/meet-people-behind-google-doodles-logo|archive-date=2014-10-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Google涂鸦最初不是动画和[[超链接|超链接]]，而是与主题相关的静态图片。但自2010年代开始，涂鸦出现的频率及其复杂程度都有所增加。2010年1月，第一个动画涂鸦推出，这个涂鸦是纪念[[艾萨克·牛顿|艾萨克·牛顿]]的。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/google/6933008/Isaac-Newtons-birth-marked-by-Google-Doodle.html|publisher=The Telegraph|date=2010-01-04|accessdate=2014-09-30|title=Isaac Newton's birth marked by Google Doodle|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006124707/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/google/6933008/Isaac-Newtons-birth-marked-by-Google-Doodle.html|archive-date=2014-10-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>不久后，第一个交互式涂鸦推出，以纪念[[吃豆人|吃豆人]]诞生30周年<ref>{{Cite web |last=Nelson |first=Randy |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2010/05/21/google-celebrates-pac-mans-30th-with-playable-logo/ |title=Google celebrates Pac-Man's 30th anniversary with playable logo |publisher=Joystiq |date=2010-05-21 |accessdate=2014-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006130544/http://www.joystiq.com/2010/05/21/google-celebrates-pac-mans-30th-with-playable-logo/ |archive-date=2014-10-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。涂鸦中也开始加入超链接，里面的超链接通常链接到涂鸦主题的[[搜索结果页|搜索结果页]]。截至2014年，Google已经在其网页上发表2000个区域和国际涂鸦。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-27732237|title=Google blunder over D-Day doodle|accessdate=2014-09-30|date=2014-06-06|publisher=BBC News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016072914/http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-27732237|archive-date=2014-10-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>

