==爭議與批評==
{{see also|對Google的批評}}
2007年9月13日，Google在[[羅爾德·達爾|羅爾德·達爾]]生日當天發佈了紀念達爾的塗鴉作品。然而，這一天碰巧是[[猶太新年|猶太新年]]。由於達爾的反以色列背景，Google此舉招致了部分群體的批評。當天下午2:00，Google從首頁移除了此塗鴉，而其塗鴉專頁上亦无法找到此涂鸦。<ref>{{cite web|author=Brown, Eliot|url=http://www.nysun.com/national/google-criticized-for-honoring-anti-israel-author/62602/|title=Google Criticized for Honoring 'Anti-Israel' Author on Rosh Hashanah|work=[[紐約太陽報|The New York Sun]]|date=2007-09-13|accessdate=2015-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150317071303/http://www.nysun.com/national/google-criticized-for-honoring-anti-israel-author/62602/|archive-date=2015-03-17|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.google.com/doodles?q=Roald%20Dahl|title=Google Doodles|publisher=|access-date=2017-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009161428/https://www.google.com/doodles?q=Roald%20Dahl|archive-date=2016-10-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，最開始Google還被批評沒有在美國愛國節日，如[[亡兵紀念日|亡兵紀念日]]和[[退伍军人节|退伍军人节]]製作塗鴉作品。<ref>{{cite news | author = Puzzanghera, Jim | url = http://www.latimes.com/business/la-fi-google9oct09,0,2321354.story?coll=la-home-center | title = Tweaks send Google critics into orbit | work = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | date = 2007-10-09 | accessdate = 2015-06-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110604110159/http://www.latimes.com/business/la-fi-google9oct09,0,2321354.story?coll=la-home-center | archive-date = 2011-06-04 | dead-url = no }}</ref>2007年，Google則製作了紀念退伍军人节的塗鴉。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.google.com/holidaylogos07.html |title=More Google: Holiday Logos |publisher=Google.com |date= |accessdate=2010-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090524140326/http://www.google.com/holidaylogos07.html |archive-date=2009-05-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年3月31日，Google被批評在當天沒有在其美國首頁發佈紀念[[復活節|復活節]]的塗鴉，而是發佈了紀念{{tsl|en|Cesar Chavez|凱薩·查維斯|凱薩·查維斯}}生日的塗鴉。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/comic-riffs/post/cesar-chavez-doodle-google-criticized-for-not-marking-easter-company-says-its-difficult-for-us-to-choose/2013/03/31/ce3da35a-9a3b-11e2-9bda-edd1a7fb557d_blog.html|title=Google criticized for not marking Easter; company says 'it's difficult for us to choose'|work=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]]|accessdate=2015-06-17|date=2013-03-31|last=Cavna|first=Michael|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150404234650/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/comic-riffs/post/cesar-chavez-doodle-google-criticized-for-not-marking-easter-company-says-its-difficult-for-us-to-choose/2013/03/31/ce3da35a-9a3b-11e2-9bda-edd1a7fb557d_blog.html|archive-date=2015-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年，Google又因只發佈紀念日本[[围棋|围棋]]手的塗鴉而未發佈诺曼底登陆70週年的塗鴉受到公眾批評。<ref name=dday>{{cite web|author=Mulshine, Molly|url=http://observer.com/2014/06/doh-google-deletes-non-d-day-doodle/|title=D'oh: Google Deletes Non-D-Day Doodle|work={{tsl|en|The New York Observer||The New York Observer}}|date=2014-06-06|accessdate=2017-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160601055011/http://observer.com/2014/06/doh-google-deletes-non-d-day-doodle/|archive-date=2016-06-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>为回应批评，Google删除了该标志，并为諾曼底入侵的图片添加了一系列链接。<ref name=dday/>而一项研究表明，Google大多数涂鸦紀念的都是[[白人|白人]]和[[男性|男性]]，而與[[妇女|妇女]]或有色人種相關的塗鴉較少，Google也因此受到批评。Google稱正著手解决這個问题。<ref>{{cite web|author= Grinberg, Emanuella|url= http://www.cnn.com/2014/06/04/living/google-doodles-diversity/|title= Why You're Seeing More Women and People of Color Google Doodles|publisher= [[CNN|CNN]]|date= 2014-06-05|accessdate= 2015-06-17|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150515113406/http://www.cnn.com/2014/06/04/living/google-doodles-diversity/|archive-date= 2015-05-15|dead-url= no}}</ref>

2016年5月19日，Google在美國首頁上發佈了紀念日裔美籍人權活動家[[河內山百合|河內山百合]]的塗鴉。<ref name="Vox">{{cite web|url=http://www.vox.com/2016/5/19/11713686/yuri-kochiyama|title=Yuri Kochiyama, today's Google Doodle, fought for civil rights — and praised Osama bin Laden|accessdate=2016-05-19|date=2016-05-19|last=Matthews|first=Dylan|publisher=Vox|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160520033506/http://www.vox.com/2016/5/19/11713686/yuri-kochiyama|archive-date=2016-05-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="TDC">{{cite web|url=http://dailycaller.com/2016/05/19/google-honors-bin-laden-supporter-with-google-doodle/|title=Google Honors Bin Laden Supporter With Google Doodle|date=2016-05-19|accessdate=2016-05-19|last=Neff|first=Blake|work=The Daily Caller|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160520122117/http://dailycaller.com/2016/05/19/google-honors-bin-laden-supporter-with-google-doodle/|archive-date=2016-05-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="WaPo">{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-fix/wp/2016/05/19/google-commemorates-a-very-controversial-civil-rights-figure-yuri-kochiyama/|title=Google commemorates a very controversial civil-rights figure, Yuri Kochiyama|work=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]]|accessdate=2016-05-19|date=2016-05-19|last=Ross|first=Janell|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160520131834/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-fix/wp/2016/05/19/google-commemorates-a-very-controversial-civil-rights-figure-yuri-kochiyama/|archive-date=2016-05-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>由於河內山百合曾發表一些爭議性觀點，如對[[奥萨马·本·拉登|奥萨马·本·拉登]]和[[毛泽东|毛泽东]]表示崇拜，Google的這一舉措遭到了批評。<ref name="Vox" /><ref name="TDC" /><ref>{{cite web|last1=Lee|first1=Edmund|title=Google celebrated civil rights leader Yuri Kochiyama and some people think it's promoting radicalism|url=http://www.recode.net/2016/5/19/11713478/google-civil-rights-yuri-kochiyama-radicalism|website=Recode|accessdate=2016-05-20|date=2016-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160520120522/http://www.recode.net/2016/5/19/11713478/google-civil-rights-yuri-kochiyama-radicalism|archive-date=2016-05-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>美國參議員[[帕特·图米|帕特·图米]]表示Google應向公眾致歉。<ref>{{cite news |last=Trujillo |first=Mario |title=GOP senator slams Google for tribute to controversial civil rights figure |url=http://thehill.com/policy/technology/280674-gop-senator-knocks-google-for-celebrating-controversial-civil-rights |work=[[国会山报|The Hill]] |date=2016-05-20 |accessdate=2016-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160523084346/http://thehill.com/policy/technology/280674-gop-senator-knocks-google-for-celebrating-controversial-civil-rights |archive-date=2016-05-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>但Google沒有正面回應此批評，亦沒有在首頁及塗鴉專頁移除這個塗鴉。<ref>{{citeweb|title=Yuri Kochiyama's 95th Birthday|url=https://www.google.com/doodles/yuri-kochiyamas-95th-birthday|publisher=Google, Inc.|accessdate=2016-09-03|date=2016-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160819055048/http://www.google.com/doodles/yuri-kochiyamas-95th-birthday|archive-date=2016-08-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>

